{"tid":899654,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"分享一件係日本七仔做收銀既小事","createTime":"2018-11-12T15:26:36.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-12T16:03:48.000Z","uid":30826,"like":4,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"b87db73f2fdebdc297fa7b7c4a2824c8ddb2605a","tid":899654,"uid":30826,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-12T15:26:36.000Z","msg":"我細細個既志願就係去日本做牛郎既 <br />\n點知去到日本鴨又做唔成(中間發生左好多事，呢D有人想知先再講)<br />\n錢又洗哂  咪唯有去七仔做住收銀先<br />\n有晚有條仔傾住電話入黎買野 仲要講廣東話既 <br />\n佢唔知我識廣東話 仲一直大大聲傾食咩催情朱古力 大家出左幾多次 <br />\n唉 原來又係一個死基佬<br />\n過左一陣 有條女黎埋 個男仔即刻收線 <br />\n最後買左堆關東煮呀炸雞呀飯團呀同埋一盒套走<br />\n姣西遇著基佬客 佢兩個都未俾錢已經開始攬攬錫錫互摷 即係我無到咁啦<br />\n我咪諗住俾D教訓佢 用拮關東煮枝籤大大力咁係個CONDOM盒度一野桶穿哂佢<br />\n依家有少少內疚 希望佢兩個唔好因爲咁攪大個肚啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cd8cf502eb651e35a1e7710f3f93a5876d646d36","tid":899654,"uid":30098,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-12T15:28:55.000Z","msg":"1.5/10"},{"pid":"a09b6d37ff29efa5b79a22d62e35f2ed60c40c85","tid":899654,"uid":96941,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-12T15:29:18.000Z","msg":"嗯嗯"},{"pid":"e98dba734b875915d425bb7a25186c6c14edbd5e","tid":899654,"uid":196701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"cd8cf502eb651e35a1e7710f3f93a5876d646d36","tid":899654,"uid":30098,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-12T15:28:55.000Z","msg":"1.5/10"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-12T15:59:01.000Z","msg":"咁高分？"},{"pid":"8c49b43bd5fea4ee6e8229af2d253e7bc74ac1e2","tid":899654,"uid":1724,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-12T16:00:43.000Z","msg":"無是咁的<br />\n0/10"},{"pid":"b6f55ede340ab7e34bb27269ad5da04aee155303","tid":899654,"uid":63734,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-12T16:03:48.000Z","